column16: Christian Yelich grounds out, pitcher Gerardo Concepcion to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Martin Prado doubles (16) on a fly ball to center fielder Jason Heyward.   Derek Dietrich scores.    Miguel Rojas scores.    Ichiro Suzuki scores.
Ichiro Suzuki walks.   Miguel Rojas to 2nd.
J.  T.   Realmuto pops out to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Derek Dietrich out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Willson Contreras.   Giancarlo Stanton scores.
Justin Bour doubles (10) on a line drive to left fielder Willson Contreras.   Christian Yelich scores.    Giancarlo Stanton to 3rd.
Matt Carpenter lines out to center fielder Albert Almora Jr.
Adam Wainwright called out on strikes.
Kolten Wong lines out sharply to shortstop Addison Russell.
